    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场惊险的冒险横跨两个交织的时间线——1797年与1927年——你必须拼凑出支离破碎的过去。在这个以独立DLC形式讲述的故事中，你能否拼合历史的残卷？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335350/extras/076d8c71863f37ca5abdcf1116b27c38.poster.avif?t=1758882188\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335350/extras/076d8c71863f37ca5abdcf1116b27c38.webm?t=1758882188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>分裂的时间线</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在1797年登上末日死神号，与海盗、隐秘的宝藏以及被诅咒的遗物一同扬帆起航。触摸一枚达布隆金币，你将快进到1927年并掘出昔日的沉船残骸。化身无畏的历史学家，在废墟中细致发掘真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>摇摆不定的忠诚</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被诅咒的海域上，暗流涌动，矛盾爆发于甲板之上。一场哗变引发了血腥的结局，也同时揭开了新的杀戮序幕，你将从令人战栗的遗骸中追寻真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335350/extras/905f1db1b56009241f0427832bf1eaca.poster.avif?t=1758882188\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335350/extras/905f1db1b56009241f0427832bf1eaca.webm?t=1758882188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>启航迎接四个全新场景</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上航程，经历四个彼此交织、笼罩在谜团中的全新场景。故事将跨越多种多样的场景，从埋藏宝物的孤岛到险象环生的海盗船——在那里，任何敢于挑战的冒险者将直面无可逃避的诅咒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拼合藏宝图</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若要横渡七海，必须先解开谜题。将古老羊皮卷的碎片拼合成一张地图，让它指引你夺取令人垂涎的宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335350/extras/ed86e2aa4aaa3c36bf3955af648c95f4.poster.avif?t=1758882188\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335350/extras/ed86e2aa4aaa3c36bf3955af648c95f4.webm?t=1758882188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>被诅咒的宝藏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追溯被掠夺的财宝，跨越130年的诅咒涟漪——被窃的财富终将引向毁灭。这份诅咒能否被打破，还是注定延续至永恒？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
